{# partenaires-section.html.twig #}

<section id="partenaires" class="py-16 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Fond à motifs provençaux stylisés -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10 z-0">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-repeat" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fond coloré -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 via-orange-300 to-lime-300 opacity-40 z-0"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        <!-- En-tête de section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wide text-lime-800 uppercase">Nos Partenaires</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl sm:tracking-tight">
                Producteurs Locaux & Passionnés
            </p>
            <p class="max-w-xl mt-5 mx-auto text-xl text-gray-800">
                Nous collaborons avec les meilleurs producteurs de Provence pour vous offrir des saveurs authentiques et fraîches.
            </p>

            <!-- Séparateur décoratif festif -->
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
                <div class="h-1.5 w-40 bg-gradient-to-r from-lime-600 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cartes des partenaires -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-10">

            <!-- Partenaire 1 -->
            <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:rotate-1 hover:shadow-xl relative">
                <!-- Élément décoratif -->
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 h-20 w-20 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>

                <!-- Image du producteur -->
                <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                            src="{{ asset('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591067716294-0d85a477d390?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') | default('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591067716294-0d85a477d390?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') }}"
                            alt="Domaine des Oliviers"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    >
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-lime-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
                        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg py-2 px-3 inline-block">
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-lime-700">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block h-4 w-4 mr-1 -mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                                </svg>
                                à 12 km de votre foodtruck
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contenu -->
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Domaine des Oliviers</h3>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800">
              <svg class="-ml-0.5 mr-1.5 h-2 w-2 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 8 8">
                <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="3" />
              </svg>
              Depuis 1987
            </span>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Marie et Jean cultivent les meilleures olives de la région. Leur huile d'olive extra vierge est pressée à froid et a remporté plusieurs prix régionaux.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Produits fournis -->
                    <div class="mt-5">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wider">Produits que nous utilisons:</h4>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                            <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Huile d'olive</span>
                            <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Olives noires</span>
                            <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Tapenade</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Partenaire 2 -->
            <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:rotate-1 hover:shadow-xl relative md:mt-6">
                <!-- Élément décoratif -->
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 h-20 w-20 bg-red-400 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>

                <!-- Image du producteur -->
                <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                            src="{{ asset('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598512752271-33f913a5af13?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') | default('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598512752271-33f913a5af13?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') }}"
                            alt="Ferme du Soleil"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    >
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-lime-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
                        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg py-2 px-3 inline-block">
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-lime-700">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block h-4 w-4 mr-1 -mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                                </svg>
                                à 8 km de votre foodtruck
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contenu -->
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Ferme du Soleil</h3>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-lime-100 text-lime-800">
              <svg class="-ml-0.5 mr-1.5 h-2 w-2 text-lime-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 8 8">
                <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="3" />
              </svg>
              Agriculture Bio
            </span>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Sophie cultive des légumes bio avec amour et passion. Ses tomates et herbes aromatiques sont reconnues pour leur goût exceptionnel et leur fraîcheur.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Produits fournis -->
                    <div class="mt-5">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wider">Produits que nous utilisons:</h4>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                            <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Tomates</span>
                            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Herbes fraîches</span>
                            <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Courgettes</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Partenaire 3 -->
            <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden transition transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:rotate-1 hover:shadow-xl relative">
                <!-- Élément décoratif -->
                <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 h-20 w-20 bg-lime-400 rounded-full opacity-20"></div>

                <!-- Image du producteur -->
                <div class="relative h-64 overflow-hidden">
                    <img
                            src="{{ asset('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1452195100486-9cc805987862?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') | default('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1452195100486-9cc805987862?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80') }}"
                            alt="Fromagerie des Alpilles"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                    >
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-lime-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4">
                        <div class="bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg py-2 px-3 inline-block">
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-lime-700">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="inline-block h-4 w-4 mr-1 -mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                                </svg>
                                à 15 km de votre foodtruck
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contenu -->
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Fromagerie des Alpilles</h3>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-purple-100 text-purple-800">
              <svg class="-ml-0.5 mr-1.5 h-2 w-2 text-purple-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 8 8">
                <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="3" />
              </svg>
              Artisanal
            </span>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Marc est un maître fromager qui perpétue la tradition familiale. Ses fromages de chèvre sont fabriqués selon des méthodes traditionnelles, avec du lait de chèvres élevées en liberté.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Produits fournis -->
                    <div class="mt-5">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 uppercase tracking-wider">Produits que nous utilisons:</h4>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                            <span class="bg-lime-100 text-lime-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Fromage de chèvre</span>
                            <span class="bg-lime-100 text-lime-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Brousse</span>
                            <span class="bg-lime-100 text-lime-800 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded">Yaourt artisanal</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Élément décoratif bas de page -->
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-20">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full animate-bounce delay-100"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-400 rounded-full animate-bounce delay-200"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-lime-400 rounded-full animate-bounce delay-300"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-bounce delay-400"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-purple-400 rounded-full animate-bounce delay-500"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>